  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Aim: To investigate whether ER stress is implicated in the pathogenesis of various pulmonary
      disorders

      Measurement:

        1. Unfolded protein responses (UPRs) in blood (PBMCs)of patients

             1. CHOP

             2. GRP 78 and so on

        2. Unfolded protein responses (UPRs) in blood (PBMCs)of healthy controls

             1. CHOP

             2. GRP 78 and so on
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
